## Why this is optimized
- **`[SerializeField]` Injection**: Replaced potential `FindObjectOfType` or `GetComponent` calls in `Awake` or `Start` with `[SerializeField]` attributes. This makes dependencies explicit in the Inspector, improving clarity and performance by avoiding runtime searches.
