- The `DropItem()` method uses `Awaitable.NextFrameAsync()` to wait for the next frame before dropping the item, reducing the load on the main thread.
- The `Rigidbody.linearVelocity` property is used to set the velocity of the dropped item, providing more precise control over the item's movement.
- The `Transform.SetParent(null)` method is used to remove the item from the hand slot, allowing it to fall freely.
